OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777209066
OL,3,CTramlines boss 'disappointed' after
OL,4,Cvandals target trees at Hillsborough
OL,5,Cpark
OL,7,FThe operations manager of Tramlines
OL,8,FFestival has said he is 'hugely
OL,9,Fdisappointed' after trees funded by
OL,10,Fthe festival have been targeted by
OL,11,Fvandals.
OL,13,FThe team who care for Hillsborough
OL,14,FPark, Sheffield Parks and Countryside,
OL,15,Fdiscovered the snapped trees earlier
OL,16,Fthis week.
OL,18,FIn a statement a spokesperson said:
OL,19,F"We're sad to report that several
OL,20,Frecently planted trees in Hillsborough
OL,21,FPark have been vandalised.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777209066
OL,3,CTramlines boss 'disappointed' after
OL,4,Cvandals target trees at Hillsborough
OL,5,Cpark
OL,7,F"These trees were planted in
OL,8,Fpartnership with Tramlines marking
OL,9,Ftheir love for the park with help from
OL,10,Four hard working volunteers, to
OL,11,Fprovide benefits for people and
OL,12,Fwildlife long into the future."
OL,14,FThe festival welcomes around 40,000
OL,15,Fvisitors and takes place in July.
OL,17,FTimm Cleasby, Operations manager of
OL,18,FTramlines Festival said: "Obviously
OL,19,Fwe're hugely disappointed that this
OL,20,Fhas happened to the trees.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777209066
OL,3,CTramlines boss 'disappointed' after
OL,4,Cvandals target trees at Hillsborough
OL,5,Cpark
OL,7,FHe added: "You know, as a team, we
OL,8,Ftake quite a lot of pride in what we
OL,9,Fdo with the park and we try and look
OL,10,Fafter it the best we can."
OL,12,FMr Cleasby added that Tramlines are
OL,13,Fworking alongside the parks team to
OL,14,Ffind a way to either repair or replace
OL,15,Fthe trees.
OL,17,FSheffield Parks and Countryside added:
OL,18,F"Repairing this damage costs time and
OL,19,Fmoney that could otherwise be spent
OL,20,Fplanting and caring for more trees
OL,21,Facross the city.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
